<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Building</title>
<para> <mcss:class xmlns:mcss="http://mcss.mosra.cz/doxygen/" mcss:class="m-note m-warning" /></para>
<para><parblock><para>All you need CMake &gt; 3.18.0 and a C++14 compliant compiler. </para>
</parblock></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>clone<sp/>--recursive<sp/>git@github.com:Pressio/pressio-tutorials.git</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">export<sp/>CXX=&lt;path-to-your-CXX-compiler&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>pressio-tutorials<sp/>&amp;&amp;<sp/>mkdir<sp/>build<sp/>&amp;&amp;<sp/>cd<sp/>build</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release<sp/>..</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">make<sp/>-j4</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para> <mcss:class xmlns:mcss="http://mcss.mosra.cz/doxygen/" mcss:class="m-note m-info" /></para>
<para><parblock><para>Individual executables for all tutorials are built inside the build subdirectory. </para>
</parblock></para>
</sect1>
